---
title: Sesame Crumbed Japanese Tofu with Udon Noodle Stir-Fry
description: We are all familiar with the 4 tastes… sweet, salty, bitter and sour. But, did you know there is a fifth taste, umami...!? It comes from the Japanese word for ‘delicious’ and is used to describe the savoury and meaty flavours.  Tonight’s meal is big on umami – so go on, get stuck in and enjoy all the delicious flavour!
